{"ID":270239, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"239\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs238.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs240.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 239<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">and keep it all in silence, not even mention them again;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> then you will be established in power,\n  virtue,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and holiness, and the wrath of God will be turned away.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Guard the Tongue<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span><\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I have one request to make of the President and members of the society, that you search\n  yourselves&mdash;the tongue is an unruly member<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span>&mdash;hold your tongues about things of no moment&mdash;a\n  little tale will set the world on fire.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> At this time, the truth on the guilty should not be told openly,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span>\n  strange as this may seem, yet this is a policy. We must use precaution in bringing sinners to justice,\n  lest in exposing these heinous sins we draw the indignation of a Gentile world upon us (and, to their\n  imagination, justly too). It is necessary to hold an influence in the world, and thus spare ourselves\n  an extermination; and also accomplish our end in spreading the Gospel, or holiness, in the earth. If\n  we were brought to desolation, the disobedient would find no help. There are some who are\n  obedient, yet men cannot steady the ark<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span>&mdash;my arm cannot do it&mdash;God must steady it. To the\n  iniquitous show yourselves merciful.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">I am advised by some of the heads of the Church to tell the Relief Society to be virtuous, but\n  to save the Church from desolation and the sword;<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> beware, be still, be prudent,<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> repent, reform, but\n  do it in a way not to destroy all around you.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> I do not want to cloak iniquity&mdash;all things contrary\n  to the will of God,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> should be cast from us, but don&rsquo;t do more hurt than good, with your\n  tongues&mdash;be pure in heart.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> Jesus designs to save the people out of their sins.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> Said Jesus, &ldquo;Ye shall\n  do the work, which ye see me do.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> These are the grand key-words<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> for the society to act upon. If\n  I were not in your midst to aid and counsel you, the devil would overcome you.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> I want the innocent\n  to go free&mdash;rather spare ten iniquitous among you, than condemn one innocent one.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> &ldquo;Fret not\n  thyself because of evildoers.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> God will see to it. (May 26, 1842.) DHC 5:19-21.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">MINUTES OF MEETING OF THE FEMALE RELIEF SOCIETY,<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">AT THE GROVE, NAUVOO, JUNE 9, 1842<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">(Reported by Miss E. R. Snow)<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Principle of Mercy<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">President Joseph Smith opened the meeting by prayer, and then addressed the congregation on\n  the design of the insti-<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114097\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114097)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114097)\">D&amp;C 58:42<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110489\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110489)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110489)\">2 Pet. 1:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106539\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106539)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106539)\">2 Chr. 30:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110362\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110362)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110362)\">James 3:5-8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110366\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110366)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110366)\">James 3:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110364\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110364)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110364)\">James 3:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108108\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108108)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108108)\">Matt. 18:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113506\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113506)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113506)\">D&amp;C 28:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113779\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113779)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113779)\">D&amp;C 42:88<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106496\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106496)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106496)\">1 Chr. 13:9-10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114759\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114759)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114759)\">D&amp;C 85:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107222\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107222)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107222)\">Isa. 51:19<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107927\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107927)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107927)\">Matt. 10:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115647\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115647)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115647)\">D&amp;C 111:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108018\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108018)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108018)\">Matt. 13:29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111729\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111729)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111729)\">Mosiah 27:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111748\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111748)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111748)\">Alma 1:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112083\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112083)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112083)\">Alma 30:7<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112297\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112297)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112297)\">Alma 41:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114755\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114755)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114755)\">D&amp;C 85:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107820\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107820)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107820)\">Matt. 5:8<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112438\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112438)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112438)\">Hel. 5:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107757\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107757)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107757)\">Matt. 1:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108800\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108800)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108800)\">John 14:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111319\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111319)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111319)\">2 Ne. 31:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112640\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112640)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112640)\">3 Ne. 18:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112709\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112709)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112709)\">3 Ne. 27:21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116249\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116249)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116249)\">D&amp;C 130:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114419\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114419)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114419)\">D&amp;C 76:31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">